**Discover Why Colour Lounge Academy is Amritsar’s Premier Choice! 🌟**

In our latest reel, founder and director Mrs. Chandni Sachdeva reveals what sets Colour Lounge apart. With 18 years of industry expertise, Colour Lounge is a luxury brand in makeup, beauty, and education. Our academy stands out with certifications valid across 140 countries and affiliations with renowned brands like L’Oréal and CIBTAC.

At Colour Lounge, we welcome students of all ages, from those who have completed 8th grade to 10th pass and beyond. We offer 100% job assistance and freelancing opportunities throughout their training. Our graduates have built successful careers globally, in countries like Canada, the USA, Australia, Dubai, and more.

Our academy provides diverse career opportunities in fields such as airport and cruise line work, the film industry, backstage roles, client handling, and social media marketing. We are committed to bringing the latest trends and techniques from around the world to our students, ensuring they receive the best possible education and career prospects.

Join Colour Lounge Academy and take the first step toward a bright and glamorous future! ✨
